### Bookmarks API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Get all bookmarks
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks

### Create a new bookmark
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Example Bookmark",
  "url": "https://example.com",
  "groupIds": []
}

### Create a bookmark with groups
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "NestJS Documentation",
  "url": "https://docs.nestjs.com",
  "groupIds": ["group-id-1", "group-id-2"]
}

### Update a bookmark
PUT {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks/{{bookmarkId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Bookmark Name",
  "url": "https://updated-url.com",
  "groupIds": ["group-id-1"]
}

### Delete a bookmark
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks/{{bookmarkId}}

### Groups API

### Get all groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/groups

### Create a new group
POST {{baseUrl}}/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Development",
  "color": "#3b82f6"
}

### Create another group
POST {{baseUrl}}/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Design",
  "color": "#ef4444"
}

### Update a group
PUT {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Group Name",
  "color": "#10b981"
}

### Delete a group
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}

### Group-Bookmark Relationships

### Add a bookmark to a group
POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/bookmarks/{{bookmarkId}}

### Remove a bookmark from a group
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/bookmarks/{{bookmarkId}}

### Example Workflow: Create group, create bookmark, add bookmark to group

### Step 1: Create a group
# @name createGroup
POST {{baseUrl}}/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Frontend Resources",
  "color": "#8b5cf6"
}

### Step 2: Create a bookmark (use the group ID from step 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vue.js Documentation",
  "url": "https://vuejs.org",
  "groupIds": ["{{groupId}}"]
}

### Step 3: Or add bookmark to group separately
POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/bookmarks/{{bookmarkId}}

